now Create an admin panel using with Edge.js templating engine with the following specifications:
- Edge.js (edge.js) templating engine
- connect-flash for flash messages
- tailwind  for UI
- DataTables for table management
- Chart.js for dashboard analytics

**Features Required:**

**1. Login Page (login.edge):**
- Modern login form with username/password
- Flash messages for errors
- Session-based authentication
- Redirect to dashboard on success

**2. Dashboard (index.edge):**
- Total admissions count
- Pending admissions count
- Total gallery images count
- Recent 5 admissions table
- Charts showing:
  * Admissions by course (pie chart)
  * Admissions by month (line chart)
  * Category distribution (bar chart)

**3. Admissions Management:**
- list.edge: DataTable with search, sort, pagination
  * Columns: ID, Name, Email, Phone, Course, Status, Actions
  * Actions: View, Edit, Delete, Change Status
  * Filter by status (pending/approved/rejected)
  * Export to CSV/Excel
- view.edge: Full admission details in organized sections
  * Personal Info
  * Parent Info
  * Address Info
  * Educational Qualifications
  * Passport photo preview
  * Status change dropdown
- edit.edge: Pre-filled form to edit admission details

**4. Gallery Management:**
- list.edge: Grid view with image thumbnails
  * Show: image, title, category
  * Actions: Edit, Delete, Reorder
  * Filter by category
  * Drag-and-drop reordering
- create.edge: Upload form with preview
  * Image upload with preview
  * Title, category, description fields
  * Client-side validation
- edit.edge: Edit existing gallery item

**5. Layout Components:**
- Sidebar navigation with active state
- Top navbar with user info and logout
- Responsive design (mobile-friendly)
- Flash message component (success, error, info)

